  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6170690/" class="title-link">看了开始一部分，就不想看下去了</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6170690"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/74346154/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/74346154/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">大批莎</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-07-19"
      class="main-meta">2013-07-19 10:45:22</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6170690_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  因为这本书还在宣传虚假的历史。还在说东北丢了是因为蒋介石不抵抗命令。其实，蒋介石从来没下达过不抵抗命令。 东北丢了，完全是因为张学良这个草包的无能。张学良并不象我们官方宣传的那样。其实就是个花花公子。花天酒地，搞女人，吸鸦片都很在行，一打仗，就吓晕了。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6170690/#comments">(4回应)</a>
